ld\nrender the merging binaries harder to detect with planned space based\ninterferometers such as LISA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2017 06:00:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2017 14:53:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
