 these distributions are at odds with the currently\nobserved statistics on ETNOs unless the EFE quadrupole strength parameter\n$Q_{2}$ has values that are unlikely (with probability < 1$\\%$) in light of the\nCassini data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2017 11:21:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 16:49:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-05"}
